     <script type="text/javascript">
      //<![CDATA[
$(function () {

    var codropsEvents = {};

    var transEndEventNames = {
        'WebkitTransition': 'webkitTransitionEnd',
        'MozTransition': 'transitionend',
        'OTransition': 'oTransitionEnd',
        'msTransition': 'MSTransitionEnd',
        'transition': 'transitionend'
    },
        transEndEventName = transEndEventNames[Modernizr.prefixed('transition')],
        $wrapper = $('#custom-inner'),
        $calendar = $('#calendar'),
        cal,
        $month,
        $year;


    buildCodrops(buildCalendar);

    $('#custom-next').on('click', function () {
        let nextM = cal.getMonth() + 1;
        let nextY = cal.getYear();

        if (nextM == 13) {
            nextY++;
            nextM = 1;
        }

        ajaxCall(nextM, nextY);
    });
    $('#custom-prev').on('click', function () {
        let nextM = cal.getMonth() - 1;
        let nextY = cal.getYear();

        if (nextM == 0) {
            nextY--;
            nextM = 12;
        }

        ajaxCall(nextM, nextY);
    });

    $("#custom-inner").on("mouseenter", ".fc-content", function () {
        $(this).addClass('active');
    });



    //deklarace eventu na hover
    function showEvents($contentEl, dateProperties) {
        hideEvents();
        var $events = $('<div id="custom-content-reveal" class="custom-content-reveal"></div>'),
            $close;
        $events.append($contentEl.html()).insertAfter($wrapper);
        $(".fc-row").on('mouseover', hideEvents);

        var invokerleft = shown.offset().left - $(".custom-calendar-wrap").offset().left;
        var invokertop = shown.offset().top - $(".custom-calendar-wrap").offset().top;

        var bodywidth = $(".fc-body").outerWidth();
        var contentwidth = $("#custom-content-reveal").outerWidth();


        if (invokerleft + contentwidth < bodywidth) {
            $events.css({
                "left": invokerleft,
                "top": invokertop + 32
            });
        } else {
            $events.css({
                "left": bodywidth - contentwidth,
                "top": invokertop + 32
            });
        }


        $("#custom-content-reveal").mouseleave(function () {
            $(".fc-row .fc-content.active").removeClass('active');
            $("#custom-content-reveal").remove();
        });

        $(".fc-head").mouseenter(function () {
            $(".fc-row .fc-content.active").removeClass('active');
            $("#custom-content-reveal").remove();
        });
        $(".custom-calendar-wrap").mouseleave(function () {
            $(".fc-row .fc-content.active").removeClass('active');
            $("#custom-content-reveal").remove();
        });

    }
    function hideEvents() {

        $(".fc-row .fc-content.active").removeClass('active');
        var $events = $('#custom-content-reveal');
        if ($events.length > 0) {

            $events.remove();

            Modernizr.csstransitions ? $events.on(transEndEventName, function () { $(this).remove(); }) : $events.remove();

        }
    }
    function eventNumbers() {
        $(".fc-content").each(function () {
            var numberevents = $(this).find('div').children('span').length;
            $(this).attr("data-content", numberevents);

        });
    }
    function ajaxCall(month, year, callback) {
        console.log("Ajax was called for date: " + month + " " + year)
        $.ajax({
            method: "GET",
            <!--url: "/Ajax-pages/DotaceHomepageCalendar?month=" + month + "&year=" + year-->
            
            url: "/cs/Ajax-pages/DotaceHomepageCalendar?month=" + month + "&year=" + year
            
      
   
        }).done(function (data) {
            console.log("Ajax succeded");

            events = JSON.parse("[" + $(data).find("#events").html().replace(/\t|\n/g, " ").replace(/,[^,]*$/, "") + "]");


            buildCodrops(function () {
                buildCalendar(month, year);
            });

        }).fail(function () {
            console.log("Ajax failed");
            buildCalendar(month, year);
        }).always(function () {
            callback ? callback() : "";
        });
    }
    function buildCodrops(callback) {
        codropsEvents = {};
        events.forEach(function (value) {
            if (codropsEvents[value.date]) {
                codropsEvents[value.date] += value.event;
            } else {
                codropsEvents[value.date] = value.event;
            }
        });
        callback();
    }
    function buildCalendar(m, y) {

        if (m && y) {
            cal = $calendar.calendario({
                caldata: codropsEvents,
                displayWeekAbbr: true,
                month: m,
                year: y,
                onDayClick: function ($el, $contentEl, dateProperties) {

                    if ($contentEl.length > 0) {
                        showEvents($contentEl, dateProperties);
                    }

                }
            });
        } else {
            cal = $calendar.calendario({
                caldata: codropsEvents,
                displayWeekAbbr: true,
                onDayClick: function ($el, $contentEl, dateProperties) {

                    if ($contentEl.length > 0) {
                        showEvents($contentEl, dateProperties);
                    }

                }
            });
        }

        $month = $('#custom-month').html(cal.getMonthName());
        $year = $('#custom-year').html(cal.getYear());



        eventNumbers();
    }

});
//]]>
     </script>
     <script type="text/javascript">
      //<![CDATA[
createCircle("yellow2", yellowzones[1]);
createCircle("yellow3", yellowzones[2]);

setInterval(function(){
createCircle("yellow2", yellowzones[1]);
createCircle("yellow3", yellowzones[2]);
}, 100);


function createCircle(canvasID, value) {

                let canvas = document.getElementById(canvasID)
                let context = canvas.getContext('2d');

                canvas.width = $("#" + canvasID).width();
                canvas.height = $("#" + canvasID).height();

                let centerX = canvas.width / 2;
                let centerY = canvas.height / 2;
                let radius = canvas.height / 2;

                let endAngle = 2 * Math.PI;
                let lastAngle = 0;

                for(var i = 0; i < 2; i++) {
                    let segment;
                    let color;
                    if (i==0) {
                        segment = value;
                        color = "#FFD600";
                    } else {
                        segment = 1 - value;
                        color = "#F6F6FB";
                    }

                    let currentSegment = endAngle * segment;

                    let currentAngle = currentSegment + lastAngle;
                    context.beginPath();
                    context.moveTo(centerX, centerY)
                    context.arc(centerX, centerY, radius, lastAngle - (1/2 * Math.PI), currentAngle - (1/2 * Math.PI), false);
                    context.closePath();

                    lastAngle = lastAngle + currentSegment;

                    context.fillStyle = color;
                    context.fill();

                    context.lineWidth = 1;
                    context.strokeStyle = "white";
                    context.stroke();
                    context.fill();
                }
            }
//]]>
     </script>
